,Not Recommended,280040,14112035,"Posted: 22 January, 2015",all,みoƦƦoƦ ₣o父,"Hey everyone and this is my review about the game!This is a rogue like game.Interface/Menu/SettingsYou can play with a controller.There is a music volume slidebar available with %.There is a sound volume slidebar available with %.There is a brightness slidebar available with %.You can toggle between fullscreen or windowed mode.You can change the controls on the keyboard.About the game.You are playing with a lizard that is able to throw knives or cast some spells. You play this with keyboard but shoot knives with the mouse cursor. The game looks like ""legend of zelda/Binding of isaac"" as you will move into a room to room killing enemies. You can't go into a different room if the enemies are still alive. There will be shops around the levels but do becareful not to attack the shopkeeper as he will go furious and start attacking you. If you have died you will turn into a ghost and new spots will be open for you. However being a ghost is a secondary life and if you have died as a ghost. It's pretty much game over. Being a ghost form will make it a bit harder for you as there will be more enemies on the screen to fight with too. There are ""revive"" stations so you will turn back in the original form. There is alot of cash scattered around the rooms. Bpss rooms are only after 3 floors.Game is kid friendly.Game is repetitive/stale.Music is okay.Graphics are cartoony.Game is a classic roguelike game.You can unlock new characters.You can unlock new items and purchase them with gold.Boss rooms are only every 3 floors.Other things.Controller is recommended to play the game as it will be smoother.-------------------I Give this game a 5/10"
